The agentic vertical slice — one deterministic, self-contained integration scenario that ties every
overnight capability together on a FIXTURE product (labeled: no mainnet, no payment, no external user,
no production feed, no faked payout). `npm run demo:agentic-v2`.

It proves end to end, with an honest trace: (1-3) safe inspection → a typed observation set with SEEN
facts, a vision INFERRED fact (never decisive), and captured action transitions; (4) a REAL safe
browser REPLAY of the first transition through the C4 guarded egress proxy — click "Start" →
reproduced, with the full replay_started→action→observed→reproduced event chain; (5-6) fixture
"architect" missions carrying source-fact mappings; (7) deterministic validation — the grounded
mission is ACCEPTED, a mission citing a non-existent fact is REJECTED (ungrounded_fact_ref), plus the
P-GEN metrics + coverage; (8) the Concierge run beginning with tools, persisting to per-chat storage,
RESUMING after a restart, and reaching `completed` with an authoritative campaign id that came from a
tool (never a message); (9) the shadow Observation Judge V2 passing a genuine account and failing a
generic one. The trace labels every fact: 5 seen · 1 inferred · replay-reproduced · 2 used-by-mission ·
1 rejected-as-ungrounded. Gated behind DEMO_AGENTIC=1 so it never slows the normal suite.

